rows.label: qst400105_msg0001
rows.name:
This is brand-new cylinder.
Please test out at nearby Salvage Point
and tell Rurui impressions from using.

rows.label: qst400105_msg0002
rows.name:
All right, then.
Leave it to me!

rows.label: qst400105_msg0003
rows.name:
Salvage point at end of this pier is
perfect place for test new cylinder.

rows.label: qst400105_msg0004
rows.name:
Look like friend all finished.
How was new cylinder?

rows.label: qst400105_msg0009
rows.name:
Fantastic? That good to hear!
Rurui hope other salvagers feel
same way!

rows.label: qst400105_msg0011
rows.name:
But it true that not easy to get used
to new cylinder after only one use.

rows.label: qst400105_msg0012
rows.name:
Rex sure problem with cylinder and not
just bad luck? This good value cylinder,
should always fetch decent treasure!

rows.label: qst400105_msg0013
rows.name: At any rate, thanks much for help.

rows.label: qst400105_msg0014
rows.name:
If friend ever run out of cylinders,
please drop by shop any time.
We make deal!

rows.label: qst400105_msg0015
rows.name:
Also, here, give friend present of three
normal cylinder. Can use in same place
as before, meh! Happy salvaging!
